msgid ""
"There are three ways to access a menu containing this option: from the :ref:"
"`project_menu` menu, the :ref:`clips` dropdown on the Project Bin toolbar or "
"by right-clicking on a clip in the Project Bin. This menu item creates a "
"folder in the Project Bin. It is a virtual folder, not one created on your "
"hard disk.  You can use this feature to organize your Project Bin when it "
"gets very large or complex by placing clips in folders, which can then be "
"collapsed to free up space in the tree.  Existing clips in the Project Bin "
"can be moved to a folder using drag and drop.  New clips can be added "
"directly to a folder by first selecting the folder (or any clip in the "
"folder) and then choosing the :menuselection:`Add Clip` option from one of "
"the dropdown menus described above."
msgstr ""
"Hi ha tres maneres d'accedir a un menú que contingui aquesta opció: des del "
"menú :ref:`project_menu`, la llista desplegable :ref:`clips` a la barra "
"d'eines de la safata del projecte o fent clic dret en un clip a la safata "
"del projecte. Aquest element de menú crea una carpeta a la safata del "
"projecte. És una carpeta virtual, no una de creada en el disc dur. Podeu "
"usar aquesta característica per organitzar la safata del projecte quan "
"esdevé molt gros o complex situant els clips en carpetes, que es poden "
"reduir per alliberar espai a l'arbre. Els clips existents a la safata del "
"projecte es poden moure a una carpeta usant arrossegar i deixar anar. Es "
"poden afegir clips nous a una carpeta seleccionant primer la carpeta (o "
"qualsevol clip de la carpeta) i després triant l'opció"
" :menuselection:`Afegeix un clip` des d'un dels menús desplegables descrits"
" més amunt."

